PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773748974
OL,3,CMother of daughter shot dead by father
OL,4,Cin Texas says he must be held
OL,5,Caccountable
OL,7,FJane Coates, the mother of Lucy
OL,8,FHarrison, who was fatally shot by her
OL,9,Ffather in Texas, appeared on Good
OL,10,FMorning Britain, calling for her
OL,11,Fformer husband to be held to account
OL,13,FA mother whose daughter was shot dead
OL,14,Fby her father at his home in Texas
OL,15,Fjust half an hour before she was due
OL,16,Fto leave for the airport for her
OL,17,Fflight home, said her former husband
OL,18,Fshould be held accountable for her
OL,19,Fdaughter's death after he escaped
OL,20,Fcharges in the US.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773748974
OL,3,CMother of daughter shot dead by father
OL,4,Cin Texas says he must be held
OL,5,Caccountable
OL,7,FLucy Harrison, 23, had been staying
OL,8,Fwith her dad, Kris Harrison and his
OL,9,Ffamily in Prosper, Texas, when she was
OL,10,Fshot in the chest shortly before 3pm
OL,11,Fon 10 January 2025.
OL,13,FA grand jury in the US determined
OL,14,Fthere was insufficient evidence to
OL,15,Fcharge anyone in connection with
OL,16,FLucy's death, but her mother, Jane
OL,17,FCoates, told Good Morning Britain
OL,18,F(DMB) that "justice hasn't been
OL,19,Fserved" as she pressed for Harrison to
OL,20,Fbe held accountable.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773748974
OL,3,CMother of daughter shot dead by father
OL,4,Cin Texas says he must be held
OL,5,Caccountable
OL,7,FAt an inquest into Ms Harrison's death
OL,8,Fat Cheshire Coroner's Court on
OL,9,FFebruary 12, more than a year after
OL,10,Fshe was fatally shot, senior coroner
OL,11,FJacqueline Devonish ruled she died due
OL,12,Fto unlawful killing on the grounds of
OL,13,Fgross negligence manslaughter.
OL,15,FConcluding her inquest last month, Ms
OL,16,FDevonish said: "To shoot her through
OL,17,Fthe chest whilst she was standing
OL,18,Fwould have required him to have been
OL,19,Fpointing the gun at his daughter,
OL,20,Fwithout checking for bullets, and
OL,21,Fpulling the trigger.
OL,26,@xD@POU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773748974
OL,3,CMother of daughter shot dead by father
OL,4,Cin Texas says he must be held
OL,5,Caccountable
OL,7,F"I find these actions to be reckless."
OL,9,FMr Harrison, described by the coroner
OL,10,Fas a functioning alcoholic, claimed
OL,11,Fthe gun had gone off accidentally.
OL,13,FSpeaking on Good Morning Britain
OL,14,F(GMB), Ms Coates said: "We feel that
OL,15,FLucy's truth has finally been heard
OL,16,Fbecause, for so long, we had to wait
OL,17,Ffor this process before we could
OL,18,Fopenly speak about what had happened.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773748974
OL,3,CMother of daughter shot dead by father
OL,4,Cin Texas says he must be held
OL,5,Caccountable
OL,7,F"We feel that truth has been heard,
OL,8,Fbut justice hasn't been served because
OL,9,Fjustice is about accountability and
OL,10,Fconsequences, and there has been no
OL,11,Faccountability and consequences."
OL,13,FMs Coates recalled the moment she was
OL,14,Ftold her daughter died in a "tragic
OL,15,Faccident" involving a gun, but said,
OL,16,Fafter seeing her daughter's autopsy,
OL,17,Fshe rejected the idea that she died
OL,18,Ffrom an accident.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773748974
OL,3,CMother of daughter shot dead by father
OL,4,Cin Texas says he must be held
OL,5,Caccountable
OL,7,F"In those very first hours, we were
OL,8,Ftold that it was a tragic accident and
OL,9,Fthe gun had just gone off," she said.
OL,11,F"For quite a few weeks, that is what I
OL,12,Funderstood. For me, I was just in such
OL,13,Fa huge state of shock, I didn't need
OL,14,Fto know how she died at that time. For
OL,15,Fme, it was just big enough that I'd
OL,16,Flost my daughter.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773748974
OL,3,CMother of daughter shot dead by father
OL,4,Cin Texas says he must be held
OL,5,Caccountable
OL,7,FShe later added: "I'm not medically
OL,8,Ftrained, obviously, but I just knew as
OL,9,Fsoon as I saw her wound that there was
OL,10,Fno way that (an accident) could
OL,11,Fpossibly have happened."
OL,13,FShe believes Mr Harrison should have
OL,14,Fbeen more aware of the dangerous
OL,15,Fnature of the weapon, a Glock semi-
OL,16,Fautomatic handgun, which he kept
OL,17,Flocked inside a box in his bedside
OL,18,Fcabinet.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773748974
OL,3,CMother of daughter shot dead by father
OL,4,Cin Texas says he must be held
OL,5,Caccountable
OL,7,F"I don't believe he intentionally
OL,8,Fmeant to kill his daughter," Ms Coates
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,F"I accept the coroner said she
OL,12,Faccepted that he wasn't aware there
OL,13,Fwas a loaded bullet in the chamber.
OL,14,FBut my point is, he should have been
OL,15,Faware, and it's an incredibly
OL,16,Fdangerous weapon."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773748974
OL,3,CMother of daughter shot dead by father
OL,4,Cin Texas says he must be held
OL,5,Caccountable
OL,7,FMr Harrison did not attend the
OL,8,Finquest, but said in a statement that
OL,9,Fhe had a conversation about guns with
OL,10,Fhis daughter, and she asked to see the
OL,11,Fgun, having never discussed his gun
OL,12,Fownership with him before.
OL,14,FMs Coates said Ms Harrison disagreed
OL,15,Fwith him having a gun in his house and
OL,16,Fwould not have asked to see the weapon.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773748974
OL,3,CMother of daughter shot dead by father
OL,4,Cin Texas says he must be held
OL,5,Caccountable
OL,7,FShe said: "We all knew what Lucy's
OL,8,Fthoughts were about her dad having a
OL,9,Fgun in the house was. She was a young
OL,10,FBritish girl. Not being brought up in
OL,11,Fthe gun culture, she didn't understand
OL,12,Fwhy her dad wanted to have a gun.
OL,14,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773748974
OL,3,CMother of daughter shot dead by father
OL,4,Cin Texas says he must be held
OL,5,Caccountable
OL,7,F"I think everybody who knew Lucy would
OL,8,Fknow that she wouldn't want to see the
OL,9,Fgun. I think the coroner described
OL,10,FKris as a teaser in his character.
OL,12,F"I just can't understand why he felt
OL,13,Fthe need to show Lucy that gun."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773748974
OL,3,CMother of daughter shot dead by father
OL,4,Cin Texas says he must be held
OL,5,Caccountable
OL,7,FWhen asked how she felt about a US
OL,8,Fgrand jury deciding there was
OL,9,Finsufficient evidence to charge anyone
OL,10,Fwith Ms Harrison's death, Ms Coates
OL,11,Fsaid: "I've been on a huge journey
OL,12,Fsince Lucy's death. I didn't know
OL,13,Fanything at all about the Texas
OL,14,Fcriminal system, the Penal Code,
OL,15,Fanything at all about district
OL,16,Fattorneys and how that all works.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31713
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773748974
OL,3,CMother of daughter shot dead by father
OL,4,Cin Texas says he must be held
OL,5,Caccountable
OL,7,F"But I think my understanding now is
OL,8,Fthat based on the evidence that was
OL,9,Fcollected from the Prosper Police
OL,10,FDepartment, all of that evidence was
OL,11,Fcollated and passed on to the first
OL,12,Fprosecutor for the District Attorney.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31714
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773748974
OL,3,CMother of daughter shot dead by father
OL,4,Cin Texas says he must be held
OL,5,Caccountable
OL,7,F"It's the first prosecutor that then
OL,8,Freally decides as to whether or not
OL,9,Fthey feel that there is enough
OL,10,Fevidence to indict, and so it's my
OL,11,Funderstanding that the first
OL,12,Fprosecutor very much guides the grand
OL,13,Fjury, which is done in secret, so we
OL,14,Fdon't know exactly what evidence they
OL,15,Fwere shown."
OL,17,F"That is something we will never know
OL,18,Fnow."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
