PN,31715
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773748974
OL,3,CMother of daughter shot dead by father
OL,4,Cin Texas says he must be held
OL,5,Caccountable
OL,7,FThe coroner ruled that Ms Harrison was
OL,8,Fshot by her alcoholic father following
OL,9,Fa "big" argument about US President
OL,10,FDonald Trump while she was staying at
OL,11,Fhis home in Texas, a place he moved to
OL,12,Fwhen she was a child.
OL,14,FThe fashion buyer from Warrington,
OL,15,FCheshire, had been on holiday with her
OL,16,Fboyfriend, Sam Littler, and they were
OL,17,Fdue to fly back to the UK on the day
OL,18,Fher father shot Ms Harrison in the
OL,19,Fchest.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31716
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773748974
OL,3,CMother of daughter shot dead by father
OL,4,Cin Texas says he must be held
OL,5,Caccountable
OL,7,FThe court heard that Mr Harrison
OL,8,Fbought the weapon to give his family a
OL,9,F"sense of security" and, as it was for
OL,10,Fhome defence, Texas laws meant he did
OL,11,Fnot need a licence.
OL,13,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,14,Four political experts are across all
OL,15,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,16,Fto the latest episode below...
